cal context with learning, clarity and economy. - Anthony Grafton  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0https://www.aup.nl/en/publish/open-access  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aHistory (General). 7aHISTORY / Modern / 17th Century.2bisacsh  aKnowledge - Amsterdam - University - Trade - Philosophy.1 aBarlaeus, Caspar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPost, Anna-Luna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVermeulen, Corinna, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAUP eBook Package 2019z978311066152140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048540020zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048540020zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789048540020.jpg  a978-3-11-066152-1 AUP eBook Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA